    "body": "It is at least doable by\n\n``` python\nIn [28]: df = pd.DataFrame(np.arange(1, 5).reshape(2,2), index=['r1', 'r2'], columns=['c1','c2'])\n\nIn [29]: df\nOut[29]: \n    c1  c2\nr1   1   2\nr2   3   4\n\nIn [30]: df.reset_index().to_dict('list')\nOut[30]: {'c1': [1, 3], 'c2': [2, 4], 'index': ['r1', 'r2']}\n\n```\n\nand then applying `json.dumps` separately.\n"
